{
 "name": "RPlog_Siths_and_Stones_...",
 "title": "Siths and Stones",
 "summary": "On the storm-tossed beaches of Orleanon on occupied Caspar, the Jedi pilot Leo races to reach the cave where he has been hiding the ambassador's daughter Gabi, as the Imperial Grand Inquisitor Darth Venger hunts them with Probot droids, Nek battle dogs, and stormtroopers. Leo draws the Imperials' fire away from the girl, cutting down the charging Nek hounds with his lightsaber, while the feisty Gabi -- armed with venom-tipped sticks of her own making -- taunts the troopers and flings herself off the cliff into the rising tide to escape, fighting the brutal surf to reach a submerged cave. Venger leaps from his speeder bike to confront Leo blade to blade, mocking the Jedi and offering a clean death, while his trooper loses Gabi's trail beneath the waves. The duel and the girl's desperate swim hang unresolved as the session breaks off.",
